  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Clean Water for 500 Families in Cambodia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CWEF&apos;s BioSand Water Filters provide clean water to families who live in remote, rural villages in Cambodia, improving health and hygiene for families and their children. In addition to the water filters, CWEF trains families in proper maintenance of their filter, along with education on proper sanitation and hygiene, and its effect on disease prevention and overall health. With proper care and maintenance, each water filter can provide a family with clean water for more than 20 years.</narrative>
  </description>
